EXPLANATION:

W/A/S/D - Steering
    W - up
    A - left
    S - down
    D - right

L - change theme

ESC - pause the game (press a key to play again)


START THE GAME BY PRESSING A KEY.

EAT AS MANY APPLES AS POSSIBLE, BUT DON'T EAT YOURSELF!


red apple - normal apple, adds length
orange apple - halfs your tail length
magenta apple - makes you go wooosh

IF YOU DIE, THE HEAD WILL START BLINKING AND A NEW GAME-WINDOW WILL POP UP.